00:19:18,003 --> 00:19:19,533
No, there is something.

288
00:19:19,683 --> 00:19:22,043
This old dude who reeks of cigarettes knows.

289
00:19:22,283 --> 00:19:23,793
He admitted it?!

290
00:19:24,003 --> 00:19:25,792
