294
00:19:35,603 --> 00:19:36,553
Stay away from me!

295
00:19:36,554 --> 00:19:38,362
Get off of me!

296
00:19:38,363 --> 00:19:41,553
A murderer has no right to speak to me that way.

297
00:19:43,563 --> 00:19:45,563
But don't worry.

