00:21:29,573 --> 00:21:31,963
Cream puff and maritozzo.

324
00:21:32,773 --> 00:21:34,113
Shortcake.

325
00:21:35,293 --> 00:21:38,913
Cheesecake, apple pie, chocolate cake.

326
00:21:40,053 --> 00:21:41,473
Mont blanc, too.

327
00:21:41,743 --> 00:21:42,832
Ito-san.

328
00:21:42,833 --> 00:21:45,282
Ito Yayoi-san, is that all right?

329
00:21:45,283 --> 00:21:46,863
We'd like to speak with you.

